languages.text: "Вижу, тебе знакомы мои братья по вере. Раз так — тебе должно быть и известно, что нам нет числа. Истреби нас на одном мире — мы поднимем головы на десяти соседних".

languages.text: "I see you are acquainted with my brethren in faith. If so, then you must also know that we are without number. Destroy our cell on one world, and we will rear our heads on a dozen others."

languages.text: 「私の仲間と知り合いのようだな。もしそうであれば、私たちに数は関係ない。1つの惑星で私たちのセルを破壊しようものなら、私たちはもっと多くの被害を出してやる」

languages.text: “看得出来，你和我的教友已经见过面了。既然如此，你肯定也知道，我们的人无穷无尽。每当你摧毁一颗行星上的教会，我们就会将真理传播到另外十颗行星上。”

traits.speaker: ItsTime_Afterlight_Speaker

languages.text: « Je vois que vous avez fait connaissance avec mes frères en religion. Dans ce cas, vous devez aussi savoir que nous sommes légion. Détruisez notre cellule sur un monde, et nous ressurgirons sur une dizaine d'autres. »
languages.original_text: "I see you are acquainted with my brethren in faith. If so, then you must also know that we are without number. Destroy our cell on one world, and we will rear our heads on a dozen others."

traits.locale_text: « Je vois que vous avez fait connaissance avec mes frères en religion. Dans ce cas, vous devez aussi savoir que nous sommes légion. Détruisez notre cellule sur un monde, et nous ressurgirons sur une dizaine d'autres. »
traits.speaker: ItsTime_Afterlight_Speaker

languages.text: «Veo que ya has conocido a mis hermanos de la fe. Si es así, ya deberías saber que nuestros números no tienen fin. Destruye nuestra célula en un planeta y surgiremos en otros diez más».
languages.original_text: "I see you are acquainted with my brethren in faith. If so, then you must also know that we are without number. Destroy our cell on one world, and we will rear our heads on a dozen others."

traits.locale_text: «Veo que ya has conocido a mis hermanos de la fe. Si es así, ya deberías saber que nuestros números no tienen fin. Destruye nuestra célula en un planeta y surgiremos en otros diez más».
traits.speaker: ItsTime_Afterlight_Speaker

languages.text: "Ich sehe, Ihr kennt meine Glaubensbrüder bereits. Dann müsst Ihr auch wissen, dass unsere Zahl unendlich ist. Wenn Ihr eine Zelle auf einer Welt zerstört, erscheinen wir auf einem Dutzend weiterer."

languages.text: "Görüyorum ki dindaşımla tanışma şerefine nail olmuşsun. Öyleyse sayımızın sonsuz olduğunu da duymuşsundur. Sen bir dünyadaki hücremizi yok edersin, biz bir sürü dünyada baş gösteririz."
languages.original_text: "I see you are acquainted with my brethren in faith. If so, then you must also know that we are without number. Destroy our cell on one world, and we will rear our heads on a dozen others."

traits.locale_text: "Görüyorum ki inanç kardeşlerimle tanışma şerefine nail olmuşsun. Öyleyse sayımızın sonsuz olduğunu da duymuşsundur. Bir dünyadaki hücremizi yok edersin, bir düzine dünyada baş gösteririz."
traits.speaker: ItsTime_Afterlight_Speaker
